"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-remembering-shara-chandra-shaha-on-int-l-olympics-day\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now Sharad Chandra Shahadeveloped a shared vision for Nepal and the SAARC region.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 92, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22, \"end\": 29, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chandra\", \"score\": 0.992073620588228, \"rank\": 0.007237919839723129, \"text\": \"Chandra\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chandra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chandra\"}, {\"begin\": 65, \"end\": 70, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1957307550081658e-18, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shared vision\", \"from\": 44, \"to\": 59}, {\"ngram\": \"the SAARC region\", \"from\": 74, \"to\": 90}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was the first person from Nepal to serve as the vice president of the Olympic Council of Asia.\", \"from\": 93, \"to\": 190, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 122, \"end\": 127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1957307550081658e-18, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first person\", \"from\": 100, \"to\": 116}, {\"ngram\": \"the vice president\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 158}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Council\", \"from\": 162, \"to\": 181}, {\"ngram\": \"Asia\", \"from\": 185, \"to\": 189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was one of the transformative heroes of Nepali sports history.\", \"from\": 192, \"to\": 257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 235, \"end\": 241, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 0.9999999677620514, \"rank\": 2.783005847165695e-08, \"text\": \"Nepali\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the transformative heroes\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He introduced the national games and led an Olympic Movement in Nepal.\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 302, \"end\": 318, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999654091886, \"rank\": 3.459077520784881e-08, \"text\": \"Olympic Movement\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 322, \"end\": 327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1957307550081658e-18, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the national games\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shah was a visionary who embodied excellence, friendship and respect, and inspired many.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 417, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shah\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"a visionary\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 349}, {\"ngram\": \"excellence\", \"from\": 363, \"to\": 373}, {\"ngram\": \"friendship\", \"from\": 375, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He blended sports, culture and education to bring people together.\", \"from\": 418, \"to\": 484, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 429, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"culture\", \"from\": 437, \"to\": 444}, {\"ngram\": \"education\", \"from\": 449, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though his tenure as the member secretary of the National Sports Council was over before I returned home from the US after finishing my undergraduate degree in 1989, the sports fraternity remembered him as someone who had profoundly impacted Nepali sports.\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 747, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 540, \"end\": 563, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Council\", \"score\": 0.9999758496930038, \"rank\": 2.4117750037994738e-05, \"text\": \"National Sports Council\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Council\"}, {\"begin\": 605, \"end\": 607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9850908497290939, \"rank\": 0.015109382122393487, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 733, \"end\": 739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 0.9999999677620514, \"rank\": 2.783005847165695e-08, \"text\": \"Nepali\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his tenure\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"the member secretary\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 532}, {\"ngram\": \"my undergraduate degree\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 647}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports fraternity\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 678}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many would agree that he was indisputably the father of the Olympic movement in Nepal.\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 828, \"end\": 833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1957307550081658e-18, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the father\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 800}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic movement\", \"from\": 804, \"to\": 824}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His vision to emulate Baron Pierre de Coubertin's ideas of the modern day Olympic Movement within the SAARC region was brilliant.\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 967, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 885, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pierre de Coubertin\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pierre_de_Coubertin\"}, {\"begin\": 940, \"end\": 945, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Asian_Association_for_Regional_Cooperation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SAARC\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Asian_Association_for_Regional_Cooperation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Asian_Association_for_Regional_Cooperation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His vision\", \"from\": 838, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"the modern day\", \"from\": 897, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic Movement\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He truly believed in the idea that sports could change the world.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 989, \"to\": 997}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He enabled Nepal to act as a catalyst for collaboration amongst SAARC countries to celebrate sports in the region.\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1149, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1046, \"end\": 1051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1957307550081658e-18, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}, {\"begin\": 1099, \"end\": 1104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Asian_Association_for_Regional_Cooperation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"SAARC\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Asian_Association_for_Regional_Cooperation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Asian_Association_for_Regional_Cooperation\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a catalyst\", \"from\": 1062, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"collaboration\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1128, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"the region\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His extraordinary ability to look far into the distant and carry the fundamental principles of Olympism proved fruitful when the SAARC decided to organize the South Asian Games.\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1327, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His extraordinary ability\", \"from\": 1150, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"the fundamental principles\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1241}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympism\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"the SAARC\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"the South Asian Games\", \"from\": 1305, \"to\": 1326}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shaha was a passionate reader, and I would imagine that he would have memorized the Olympic Anthem played at each Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Shaha\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1334}, {\"ngram\": \"a passionate reader\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Anthem\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"each Olympic Games\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1456}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His desire to kindle the same flame in our region was his dream.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1522, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His desire\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"the same flame\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"our region\", \"from\": 1497, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"his dream\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The principles of Olympism are about driving social change that is far-reaching.\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1604, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The principles\", \"from\": 1524, \"to\": 1538}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympism\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1550}, {\"ngram\": \"social change\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1582}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What could be more apt for our region than to mobilize the masses through sports to practice non-discrimination, sustainability, humanism, universality and alliances.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1771, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our region\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"the masses\", \"from\": 1660, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1685}, {\"ngram\": \"non-discrimination, sustainability\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1732}, {\"ngram\": \"humanism\", \"from\": 1734, \"to\": 1742}, {\"ngram\": \"universality\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1756}, {\"ngram\": \"alliances\", \"from\": 1761, \"to\": 1770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr. Thomas Back, president of the International Olympic Committee, recently said, \\\"In an increasingly individualized society which is on the other hand ever more globalized and networked, sport and sports organizations can only retain their significance if they achieve unity in diversity and base their organization and structures on the principles of respect, responsibility and reliability.\\\"\", \"from\": 1773, \"to\": 2167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1777, \"end\": 1783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"score\": 0.9755277848981811, \"rank\": 0.025016500152355372, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clarence_Thomas\"}, {\"begin\": 1807, \"end\": 1838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1799}, {\"ngram\": \"an increasingly individualized society\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"the other hand\", \"from\": 1910, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"ever more globalized and networked, sport and sports organizations\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"their significance\", \"from\": 2008, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"unity\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"diversity\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2061}, {\"ngram\": \"their organization\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2089}, {\"ngram\": \"structures\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"the principles\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2122}, {\"ngram\": \"respect\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2133}, {\"ngram\": \"responsibility\", \"from\": 2135, \"to\": 2149}, {\"ngram\": \"reliability\", \"from\": 2154, \"to\": 2165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have no doubt Shaha had understood this sentiment some four decades before.\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no doubt\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2183}, {\"ngram\": \"Shaha\", \"from\": 2184, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"this sentiment\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2219}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Developing administrators and leaders at the National Sports Council and across 75 districts still has his footprints.\", \"from\": 2246, \"to\": 2364, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2291, \"end\": 2314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Council\", \"score\": 0.9999758496930038, \"rank\": 2.4117750037994738e-05, \"text\": \"National Sports Council\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Council\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Sports_Council\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"administrators\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2271}, {\"ngram\": \"leaders\", \"from\": 2276, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"his footprints\", \"from\": 2349, \"to\": 2363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2006 during the Asian Games in Doha, I had the honor of sitting next to the honorary lifetime president of the International Olympic Committee, Juan Antonio Samaranch.\", \"from\": 2366, \"to\": 2536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2404, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7023495281636875e-18, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}, {\"begin\": 2480, \"end\": 2511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Asian Games\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2396}, {\"ngram\": \"the honor\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"the honorary lifetime president\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I introduced myself as an aspiring administrator of the Olympic Movement from Nepal.\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2593, \"end\": 2609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 0.9999999654091886, \"rank\": 3.459077520784881e-08, \"text\": \"Olympic Movement\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2615, \"end\": 2620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1957307550081658e-18, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an aspiring administrator\", \"from\": 2560, \"to\": 2585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He smiled, held my hands and said, \\\"This is a beautiful path you have chosen.\\\"\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my hands\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2646}, {\"ngram\": \"a beautiful path\", \"from\": 2666, \"to\": 2682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, he went on to inquire, \\\"How is my friend Sharad and what is he doing now and where is he?\\\"\", \"from\": 2701, \"to\": 2797, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my friend\", \"from\": 2738, \"to\": 2747}, {\"ngram\": \"Sharad\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I told him that he was well and holds a very high position within the government.\", \"from\": 2798, \"to\": 2879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very high position\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 2856}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 2864, \"to\": 2878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He then again held my hand and said, \\\"Well, do not forget to give him my best regards.\\\"\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my hand\", \"from\": 2899, \"to\": 2906}, {\"ngram\": \"my best regards\", \"from\": 2950, \"to\": 2965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This was a profound moment for me.\", \"from\": 2968, \"to\": 3002, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a profound moment\", \"from\": 2977, \"to\": 2994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2001, after having struggled for months to get permission to use Gokarna Safari Park premises from the owners to organize the Asian Cross-Country Championships being held for the first time in Nepal, I met Shaha and the owner of the Park.\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3133, \"end\": 3138, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.5560873935722213, \"rank\": 0.7925680192007234, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 3139, \"end\": 3166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NACAC_Cross_Country_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cross-Country Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NACAC_Cross_Country_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NACAC_Cross_Country_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 3200, \"end\": 3205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1957307550081658e-18, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 3040, \"to\": 3046}, {\"ngram\": \"permission\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3064}, {\"ngram\": \"Gokarna Safari Park premises\", \"from\": 3072, \"to\": 3100}, {\"ngram\": \"the owners\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3116}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 3182, \"to\": 3196}, {\"ngram\": \"Shaha\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3218}, {\"ngram\": \"the owner\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3232}, {\"ngram\": \"the Park\", \"from\": 3236, \"to\": 3244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was there to measure the course with a measuring device and it looked rather odd for someone to be carrying an instrument on wheels at a golf course.\", \"from\": 3247, \"to\": 3398, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 3270, \"to\": 3280}, {\"ngram\": \"a mea